Mix thoroughly sugar, shortening and egg. Stir in buttermilk and vanilla. Sift dry ingredients and stir in. Add nuts. Chill dough for 1 hour. Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C). Drop by rounded spoonfuls onto the cookie sheet. Bake 8 to 10 minutes. Cool. Frost with chocolate or white icing. Enjoy!